description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Plezier purrs with a rating of 78, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 78, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Nine Lives for East, Stringalong for South, and 5 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70781-29754-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
